The evidence with the title 'Did Ahmadinejad really say Israel should be 'wiped off the map ... ' says Oct 5, 2011  ... “ it was only perhaps three weeks ago that the president of Iran once again said that Israel should be eradicated off the face of the Earth . As you recall, it was about in 2005 when he [ Mahmoud Ahmadinejad] said before that Israel -- he would use a nuclear weapon to wipe Israel off the face of the earth . ”.
